**Use Case**:
- Property tax consultants managing 50+ clients on the same block
- HOA boards that want to protest for the whole subdivision
- Real estate agents advising buyers about tax exposure

**How**: Already have the bulk data. Build a batch processing endpoint + summary dashboard.

**Feasibility**: â­â­â­â­â­ â€” Mostly UI/UX work on top of existing capabilities.

