**Feasibility**: â­â­â­â­ â€” Would need a lightweight web viewer, but we have all the data.

---

#### ðŸ”” 4.8 Annual Assessment Monitor & Alert System
**What**: Users register their property â†’ we auto-check when new assessment values are published â†’ send an alert: *"Your 2027 assessment increased 14%. Based on our analysis, you have a strong case for protest."*

**How**:
- Background cron job compares Supabase records against new HCAD bulk data each year
- Email/SMS notification when assessment change exceeds a threshold
- One-click "Generate My Protest Report" from the alert

**Why It Matters**: Creates recurring engagement. Moves from one-time tool to **annual subscription** model.

**Feasibility**: â­â­â­â­ â€” Simple data comparison + notification service (SendGrid/Twilio).

